description: The construction of a part four/part five/part six storey building and part nine/part ten storey building comprising business/office (Use Class B1) floorspace, 2 one bedroom and 1 two bedroom live/work units, 94 one bedroom, 63 two bedroom self-contained flats on the 'Venson' site, Conington Road SE13, together with associated landscaping, an electricity sub-station, refuse/cycle stores and 55 car parking spaces at basement level with access onto Conington Road.
